<P>> I imagine that groups using Shamans, Monks, and Druids as tanks

<BR>&gt; will do ok, but not nearly as well as those with true tanks like
<BR>&gt; you suggested. It will be interesting in Final to see the level
<BR>&gt; race taking place. Groups such as your own will probably do well
<BR>&gt; by following such strategies to keep their members on top of the
<BR>&gt; level race.
<P>&gt; Aside from that I hope Verant fixes fighters and makes other
<BR>&gt; changes to the combat system so level does not remain the only
<BR>&gt; factor determining in the outcome of PvP battles.
<P>vjhgc
